    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Club\nMENU",
      "Bar Service\nMiniatures\nSherry\nVermouth, sweet or dry\nScotch, American and Canadian Whiskies\nGin\nRum\nVodka\nCognac\nDrambuie\nCointreau\nWines\nFrench Wine, red or white\nBeers\nEnglish beers\nLager\nChampagne is available for\npurchase on request\nLondon - Seattle\nLunch\nSalmon mayonnaise\nFlakes of poached salmon set on a bed of lettuce, dressed with\nmayonnaise and garnished with cucumber\nVeal marsala\nPan fried collops of veal finished in a rich marsala wine sauce,\nserved with buttered peas, baby carrots and noisette potatoes\nSuprême of chicken forestière\nBreast of chicken in mushroom sauce, served with a selection\nof buttered mixed vegetables and noisette potatoes\nFruit salad\nCheese. Cream crackers\nCoffee. Caffeine free coffee\nWe apologize if, due to previous passenger selection,\nyour choice is not available."
    ],
